PLACEHOLDER — replace this directory entry with a real og-image.png.

Recommended specs:
  • 1200 x 630 px
  • PNG or JPG (PNG preferred for type/logo work)
  • Under 300 KB
  • Branded: serif headline "CBSS Tutoring Services" over the navy/cream palette,
    accent amber rule. Match the site's editorial tone — no clipart.

Once you drop og-image.png into /public, social previews on Twitter, Facebook,
LinkedIn, iMessage, and Slack will render the new image automatically.
